```python
            await client.batch_removal_by_form_instance_id_list_with_options_async(batch_removal_by_form_instance_id_list_request, batch_removal_by_form_instance_id_list_headers, util_models.RuntimeOptions())
        except Exception as err:
            if not UtilClient.empty(err.code) and not UtilClient.empty(err.message):
                # err 中含有 code 和 message 属性，可帮助开发定位问题
                pass


if __name__ == '__main__':
    Sample.main(sys.argv[1:])
```

```js
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
```
